data.description: Welcome to 4535 Limerick Drive, a beautiful townhome located in the lovely neighborhood of Palmetto Cove Community. This home offers 3 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and a 1-car garage. The spacious and open floor plan of this residence creates an inviting atmosphere, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying quality time with family. The community pool is about 5 minutes walk distance. Palmetto Cove is conveniently located to I-75, I-4, groceries stores, shopping centers, restaurants, Downtown Tampa, and much more!! And last but not least... trash, sewer, water, and cable TV are included in the monthly association fees!! Don't miss the opportunity of this great deal!
